questions.quote: Oh hey, Monica, I heard you saw Donald Trump at your convention.
Monica, Monica, you could come in straddling him, they still wouldn't believe it. We're here.
Well, I relied on a carefully regimented program of denial and, and wetting the bed.
Oh my God. I cannot keep having this same fight with you Ross! Look, urrgh, maybe we should take a break.
I don't know! Joey hasn't had this much trouble getting out words since we saw him in Macbeth!
Oh my God! He's trapped in an ATM vestibule with Jill Goodacre! Chandler, listen.
I think the things that you said about me are really unfair, and I would like for you to give my bouillabaisse another chance.
You want a piece of me, sir? Is that what your saying? You want a piece of me?
Ohh forget it. Too hell with tradition, we're happy to do it.
Please don't be a space ship. Please don't be a space ship. Oh thank God! How could you be beeping?! I just disconnected you! I took out your battery! How can...
